&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary: &lt;/strong&gt;The Outreach Coordinator plays a crucial role in establishing and maintaining positive, collaborative relationships with community stakeholders. This position is primarily responsible for engaging community organizations, partners, and local leaders to promote awareness of the organization’s services and to build strategic partnerships that support and advance the mission. Through effective communication, outreach, and collaboration, the Liaison serves as a key ambassador for the organization within the community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duties and Responsibilities: &lt;/strong&gt;Duties include, but are not limited to:&lt;/p&gt;
